6
00:02:14.134 --> 00:02:16.136
[Tires Squealing]

7
00:03:24.871 --> 00:03:27.457
- Go, go, go, go!
<i>- [Alarm Blaring]</i>

8
00:03:27.541 --> 00:03:30.627
Move it! Move it!
Move it! Let's go!

9
00:03:30.711 --> 00:03:32.796
<i>- [Alarm Continues]
- Move it! In the car.</i>

10
00:03:34.506 --> 00:03:37.008
Let's go.

11
00:03:37.092 --> 00:03:40.011
- Let's go.
- There's four of you.

12
00:03:40.095 --> 00:03:41.930
You can count.
I'm impressed. Now drive.

13
00:03:42.013 --> 00:03:43.890
Rule one:
Never change the deal.

14
00:03:43.974 --> 00:03:47.686
The deal was transportation for three men
with a combined weight of 254 kilos.

15
00:03:47.769 --> 00:03:50.647
Yeah? Well, this
is a new deal.

16
00:03:50.731 --> 00:03:54.818
An extra 80 kilos means we'll not make
your destination on the gas I have allotted.

17
00:03:54.901 --> 00:03:57.738
<i>- So we'll stop and get more gas.</i>
- Every stop we make exposes us.

18
00:03:57.821 --> 00:04:00.574
Every exposure increases
the risk of getting caught.

19
00:04:00.657 --> 00:04:04.077
<i>An extra 80 kilos means the KONI
shock absorbers installed for this job…</i>

20
00:04:04.161 --> 00:04:08.206
will not give us the ability to outmaneuver
any police that might be chasing us.

21
00:04:08.290 --> 00:04:12.169
<i>Which means, if there is
a chase, we lose our advantage.</i>

22
00:04:12.252 --> 00:04:14.755
Which also increases the possibility
of getting caught.

23
00:04:14.838 --> 00:04:18.383
I don't want to get caught.
You don't want to get caught.

24
00:04:18.467 --> 00:04:21.261
Just drive the car, or you're gonna
catch a bullet through the brains.

25
00:04:21.344 --> 00:04:24.014
- And who's going to drive?
- Shoot this asshole! I drive!

26
00:04:24.097 --> 00:04:26.183
Not without the ignition code
you won't.

27
00:04:32.230 --> 00:04:35.484
Three men.
254 kilos.

28
00:04:35.567 --> 00:04:37.527
That was the deal.

29
00:04:39.070 --> 00:04:40.906
[Shouts]

30
00:04:43.867 --> 00:04:47.746
<i>Three men.
254 kilos.</i>

31
00:04:47.829 --> 00:04:49.790
Seat belts.

32
00:04:49.873 --> 00:04:53.210
- [Shouts]
- [Beeps]

33
00:04:53.293 --> 00:04:55.670
- [Engine Starts]
<i>- [Man Grunts]</i>

34
00:04:55.754 --> 00:04:56.713
Shit!

35
00:04:56.838 --> 00:04:58.256
[Engine Revving]

36
00:04:59.758 --> 00:05:01.718
- [Siren Wailing]
<i>- [Seat Belt Clicks]</i>

37
00:05:05.847 --> 00:05:08.183
[Siren Wailing]

38
00:05:22.113 --> 00:05:24.115
