174
00:15:16.165 --> 00:15:19.836
7:00 in the morning,
at the front door.

175
00:15:21.379 --> 00:15:26.342
A package. One meter 50 by 50.
Fifty kilos. 250 kilometers.

176
00:15:26.426 --> 00:15:28.886
Traveling within the speed limit,
one stop for refreshments...

177
00:15:28.970 --> 00:15:30.888
40,000.

178
00:15:30.972 --> 00:15:34.267
Half now, half on delivery.
Delivery will be at noon.

179
00:15:34.350 --> 00:15:37.478
If no one's there, it is not my responsibility.
I'll leave the package.

180
00:15:37.562 --> 00:15:41.274
Once we make a deal, the terms of that deal
cannot be changed or renegotiated.

181
00:15:41.357 --> 00:15:43.985
- Another rule?
- It's rule number one.

182
00:15:44.944 --> 00:15:47.655
Do we have a deal?

183
00:15:52.785 --> 00:15:56.873
- You're very precise.
- Transportation is a precise business.

184
00:16:35.870 --> 00:16:38.039
<i>- [Beeps]</i>
- [Engine Starts]

185
00:16:53.346 --> 00:16:56.641
<i>[Soft Rambling]</i>

186
00:16:58.601 --> 00:17:00.520
Flat.

187
00:17:00.603 --> 00:17:02.605
<i>♪♪ [Radio: Pop]</i>

188
00:17:03.981 --> 00:17:06.567
<i>♪♪ [Stops]</i>

