- Good girl.
- [Whimpering]

201
00:20:13.379 --> 00:20:16.382
<i>[Screaming]</i>

202
00:20:23.139 --> 00:20:26.600
<i>- [Thumping]
- [Muffled Shouts]</i>

203
00:20:32.523 --> 00:20:35.192
<i>[Screams]</i>

204
00:20:42.032 --> 00:20:44.160
<i>[Screaming Continues]</i>

205
00:20:49.039 --> 00:20:51.000
