Never open the package.

248
00:25:16.932 --> 00:25:19.643
[Laughs]
I like that.

249
00:25:19.727 --> 00:25:24.440
Rules. You can't get anything done
in a world without rules.

250
00:25:24.523 --> 00:25:26.692
You're a foreigner, right?

251
00:25:26.775 --> 00:25:29.570
It's a nice little thing
you've got goin' for yourself here.

252
00:25:29.653 --> 00:25:33.157
High-class. Good reputation.

253
00:25:33.240 --> 00:25:35.159
