258
00:25:57.389 --> 00:26:00.309
- No. No.
- That concludes the deal.

259
00:26:05.564 --> 00:26:09.276
You know, I was wondering...

260
00:26:09.359 --> 00:26:13.238
if you wouldn't mind
transporting something for me.

261
00:26:13.322 --> 00:26:15.532
That's what you do, right?

262
00:26:15.616 --> 00:26:17.993
You deliver.
No questions asked.

263
00:26:21.830 --> 00:26:24.083
- Why not?
- Mmm.

264
00:26:24.166 --> 00:26:27.002
[Chuckles]

265
00:26:27.086 --> 00:26:29.505
Weight?

266
00:26:31.090 --> 00:26:33.008
Maybe a kilo.

267
00:26:33.092 --> 00:26:35.636
- Destination.
- Grenoble.

268
00:26:35.719 --> 00:26:37.638
306 Rue du Lac.

269
00:26:37.721 --> 00:26:39.223
A Mr.-

270
00:26:39.306 --> 00:26:41.517
Oh, right. I forgot.

271
00:26:41.600 --> 00:26:43.519
Rule two.

272
00:27:01.370 --> 00:27:03.622
[Chuckles]

273
00:27:03.705 --> 00:27:05.707
I like him.

274
00:27:05.791 --> 00:27:07.709
